  "detailed_description": "You discover a pony-foundling on your porch. Will you be able to raise it to adulthood? Play, feed, care for, wash and do your best to keep your pet happy.<br>You can even create your own unique pony, Pegasus or alicorn!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Up to 12 pets<br></li><li> Advanced customization options for your pony: hairstyles, cutie marks, hats and accessories<br></li><li> 4 pony races<br></li><li> Create your home how you like: arrange furniture, paint and create new rooms<br></li><li> Lots of toys to try out<br></li><li> Achievements</li></ul>",
